00:14:42,208 --> 00:14:43,833
on the knife or
anything like that.

262
00:14:43,916 --> 00:14:46,625
Why don't you sit over
there and watch instead?

263
00:14:47,708 --> 00:14:49,541
'Kay.

264
00:14:49,625 --> 00:14:50,541
Uh hey!

265
00:14:50,625 --> 00:14:53,166
No, you'll just get in my way.

266
00:14:59,875 --> 00:15:00,958
Those guys.

267
00:15:01,041 --> 00:15:02,416
It's not fair, they
keep treating

268
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:04,708
me like I'm a little kid.

269
00:15:04,791 --> 00:15:05,916
But I'm not a kid anymore,

270
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:08,916
I'm big enough to do
plenty of things myself.

271
00:15:24,125 --> 00:15:25,708
Witch Hill, huh?

272
00:15:26,541 --> 00:15:29,458
What if a witch
really lives here?

273
00:15:29,541 --> 00:15:31,333
Maybe she's like me?

274
00:15:37,458 --> 00:15:42,166
Don't look so terrified of me,
my little witch friend...

275
00:15:42,250 --> 00:15:44,666
Hi... I'm Rubi.

276
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:46,416
I'm a witch who
lives on this hill.

277
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:47,791
A witch?

278
00:15:47,875 --> 00:15:48,875
Right.

279
00:15:48,958 --> 00:15:52,250
We're the same,
you and I Yukari.

280
00:15:52,333 --> 00:15:54,541
How do you know my name?

281
00:15:54,625 --> 00:15:56,583
You came up this afternoon.

282
00:15:56,666 --> 00:15:59,708
