...if you want?

289
00:16:14,041 --> 00:16:15,000
You...

290
00:16:15,083 --> 00:16:16,666
...you'd be my friend?

291
00:16:16,750 --> 00:16:18,666
So we can then, right?

292
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:20,416
Thank you!

293
00:16:20,500 --> 00:16:22,166
Rubi, you...

294
00:16:22,250 --> 00:16:24,000
You and I are both witches.

295
00:16:24,083 --> 00:16:26,708
So we should be best friends!

296
00:16:29,458 --> 00:16:31,041
My new friend!

297
00:16:36,375 --> 00:16:37,583
Meow.

298
00:16:37,666 --> 00:16:39,375
There's just no
substitute for the fish

299
00:16:39,458 --> 00:16:40,666
you get in the human world...

300
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:42,208
Miss, your tail!

301
00:16:42,291 --> 00:16:44,125
U-Uh look, you guys,
it's not what you think!

302
00:16:44,208 --> 00:16:45,958
I promise I was
just gonna count 'em.

303
00:16:46,041 --> 00:16:47,500
It's the truth!

304
00:16:50,541 --> 00:16:53,125
Hey.
Where'd Yukari go?

305
00:16:57,541 --> 00:16:59,208
It's so pretty, huh?

306
00:16:59,291 --> 00:17:01,958
It's really such a beautiful
hillside, it's a shame those

307
00:17:02,041 --> 00:17:04,750
humans have been trying to
tear it down for years.

308
00:17:04,833 --> 00:17:06,375
Yeah, that's right,
I heard something

309
00:17:06,458 --> 00:17:07,916
about a development project.

310
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,416
Yes.

311
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:11,458
And that's exactly why I'm
going to wipe out the humans.

312
00:17:12,541 --> 00:17:15,916
So will you help me out?
I need you.

313
00:17:17,041 --> 00:17:19,333
But, It's just...
I don't...

314
00:17:19,416 --> 00:17:22,916
Don't worry. All of the
plans are already in place.

315
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,958
All we have to do is
carry out Her Ladyship's

316
00:17:25,041 --> 00:17:27,708
orders and everything'll
work out just fine.

317
00:17:27,791 --> 00:17:29,166
"Her Ladyship?"

318
00:17:30,458 --> 00:17:31,625
Yes.
I'll show you.

319
00:17:31,708 --> 00:17:33,083
C'mon!

320
00:17:33,791 --> 00:17:36,166
The three of us'll live
together on Witch Hill.

321
00:17:36,250 --> 00:17:38,750
It'll be great!
Come!

322
00:17:38,833 --> 00:17:40,750
But... I...

323
00:17:40,833 --> 00:17:42,208
Hey!

324
00:17:43,333 --> 00:17:45,375
Oh Yukari, there you are!

325
00:17:45,458 --> 00:17:47,666
I'm glad I found you, when
you disappeared on us,

326
00:17:47,750 --> 00:17:49,291
we all got really worried.

327
00:17:49,375 --> 00:17:50,833
I'm sorry!

328
00:17:50,916 --> 00:17:52,666
Hey, who's your friend?

329
00:17:52,750 --> 00:17:54,958
Oh...
This is my--

330
00:17:55,875 --> 00:17:57,708
So you still come
to try and defile

331
00:17:57,791 --> 00:17:59,458
our lovely hillside
Human scum?!

332
00:17:59,541 --> 00:18:00,625
Rubi!

333
00:18:00,708 --> 00:18:02,083
What the...?!

334
00:18:04,875 --> 00:18:07,708
Quick monster fact these guys
are a type of plant monster

335
00:18:07,791 --> 00:18:10,833
that will attack humans or
animals and devour them, Whee!

336
00:18:13,291 --> 00:18:16,208
You've got it all wrong...!
Tsukune's not what you think!

337
00:18:16,291 --> 00:18:18,500
He didn't come here
to defile your hillside!

338
00:18:18,583 --> 00:18:20,125
Just stay out of my way, Yukari!

339
00:18:20,208 --> 00:18:22,666
No! Please!
Don't do this, he's my friend!

340
00:18:23,833 --> 00:18:25,625
Now devour him!

341
00:18:34,541 --> 00:18:36,541
No Yukari!
Don't interfere!

342
00:18:36,625 --> 00:18:38,083
I don't have any other choice!

343
00:18:38,166 --> 00:18:39,208
Why not?!

344
00:18:39,291 --> 00:18:40,583
'Cause I won't let
you hurt my friend!

345
00:18:40,666 --> 00:18:42,583
I don't understand,
he's not even a witch!

346
00:18:42,666 --> 00:18:43,750
So what?!

347
00:18:43,833 --> 00:18:46,291
Tsukune's still a
close friend of mine!

348
00:18:46,375 --> 00:18:49,416
And that's why I'm not gonna let
you touch him, you hear me?!

349
00:18:49,500 --> 00:18:50,750
Thank you, Yukari.

350
00:18:50,833 --> 00:18:52,625
Close friend?

351
00:18:52,708 --> 00:18:54,333
That can't be.

352
00:18:54,416 --> 00:18:55,666
I don't understand.

353
00:18:55,750 --> 00:18:57,541
Nothing in this world could
possibly be stronger

354
00:18:57,625 --> 00:19:00,250
than the bonds of kinship
between witches.

355
00:19:00,333 --> 00:19:01,958
If there is
something stronger...

356
00:19:02,041 --> 00:19:03,875
Then I will destroy it!

357
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:08,875
Please, stop!

358
00:19:19,250 --> 00:19:21,208
I bet that's it.

359
00:19:21,958 --> 00:19:24,916
The stories of all the people
who disappeared here.

360
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,791
They were all...

361
00:19:27,666 --> 00:19:32,083
I can't. I can't hold
on too much longer!

362
00:19:32,166 --> 00:19:34,125
What would a kid like you know?

363
00:19:35,625 --> 00:19:38,875
I can do things, too!
Just watch!

364
00:19:38,958 --> 00:19:41,541
Cause I'm not a
little kid anymore!

365
00:19:41,625 --> 00:19:43,208
Yukari, no!

366
00:20:02,208 --> 00:20:03,625
Some showdown, huh?

367
00:20:03,708 --> 00:20:05,625
Everyone's favorite
vampire Moka

368
00:20:05,708 --> 00:20:08,541
didn't even transform
this time, whee!

369
00:20:09,083 --> 00:20:10,750
Oh, wow, what are those things?!

370
00:20:10,833 --> 00:20:12,125
Monsters!

371
00:20:12,208 --> 00:20:15,208
And it looks like
Yukari took them out!

372
00:20:18,708 --> 00:20:20,083
Yukari!

373
00:20:21,791 --> 00:20:24,541
Are you all right?
Don't die on us!

374
00:20:26,333 --> 00:20:29,250
Don't worry.
Please.

375
00:20:29,333 --> 00:20:31,291
I'm just a little tired.

376
00:20:31,375 --> 00:20:32,291
Idiot!

377
00:20:32,375 --> 00:20:34,125
Why did you fight
them all alone?

378
00:20:34,208 --> 00:20:35,791
But Kurumu...!

379
00:20:36,708 --> 00:20:38,250
We can chew her out later.

380
00:20:38,333 --> 00:20:40,750
For right now, we should
get her back to the tent.

381
00:20:40,833 --> 00:20:42,208
Get on.

382
00:20:52,625 --> 00:20:54,000
Hey Rubi.

383
00:20:54,500 --> 00:20:55,750
Listen.

384
00:20:55,833 --> 00:20:58,750
I've decided that I
can't stay here with you...

385
00:20:58,833 --> 00:21:00,041
You see.

386
00:21:00,125 --> 00:21:02,708
I have friends
that I care about.

387
00:21:02,791 --> 00:21:04,166
I'm sorry.

388
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:08,166
Come on.

389
00:21:08,250 --> 00:21:10,416
Stop playing tough and let me
carry you down on my back!

390
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:12,125
No, I can walk.

391
00:21:12,208 --> 00:21:15,916
We witches are extremely good at
healing ourselves, you know.

392
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:19,666
I swear you're just too
proud to ask for help.

393
00:21:19,750 --> 00:21:22,458
Yeah, and you're too proud
to say how you feel.

394
00:21:22,541 --> 00:21:25,583
Guess that's it.
Yukari seems fine now, huh?

395
00:21:25,666 --> 00:21:28,375
Yeah. I'm really
glad everyone's okay.

396
00:21:28,458 --> 00:21:31,291
You went out looking for Yukari,
but then you didn't come back,

397
00:21:31,375 --> 00:21:32,833
either, so I got really worried

398
00:21:32,916 --> 00:21:35,000
that something might've
happened to you.

399
00:21:35,083 --> 00:21:36,458
I just...

400
00:21:37,958 --> 00:21:40,041
Moka.

401
00:21:40,125 --> 00:21:41,500
Tsukune.

402
00:21:44,333 --> 00:21:48,375
We're finally alone now.
For the first time.

403
00:22:05,666 --> 00:22:07,625
Oh, Tsukune...

404
00:22:07,708 --> 00:22:11,166
I will bring Yukari home with
me, no matter what it takes!

405
00:22:11,250 --> 00:22:13,916
'Cause it's my wish!

406
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:17,958
And also because
Her Ladyship demands it!

407
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,500
Tsukune?

408
00:22:20,583 --> 00:22:22,833
Please, no!

409
00:22:22,916 --> 00:22:25,750
Noooooooo!

410
00:22:37,083 --> 00:22:39,708
Rubi, no!
What have you done?!

411
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:46,083
How dare you!

